metadata.name: 𝕷𝕺𝕯𝕲𝕰 - 𝕸¹⁰
metadata.description:
Vintage Detroit footy shot in the 90’s on VHS-C, edited and glitched in the 20’s on custom circuit bent hardware. 

Heavy-hitting basslines and slightly ominous hat patterns dominate, leaving this cut verging on the territory of dark, minimal electro destruction… with a subtle dose of that funky boom bap. Perfectly applicable to both basement dancefloor experiments and gangster dealings alike. 

AV COLLAB:
Kero X Chris DeLuca
